Package: inspercidados
Title: Standardized Access to Brazilian Urban Public Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Insper Cidades", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
             email = "cidades@insper.edu.br"),
      person("Vinicius", "Reginatto", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides standardized, reproducible access to Brazilian public
    datasets related to urban research. All datasets are processed by
    researchers at Insper Cidades and made available through Dataverse.
    The package enables researchers to download, cite, and use these datasets
    with complete transparency and scientific reproducibility.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/insper-cidades/inspercidados
BugReports: https://github.com/insper-cidades/inspercidados/issues
